headline: Virtus Investment Partners (VRTS) Surpasses Q2 Earnings Estimates
summary: Virtus (VRTS) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +0.64% and -0.38%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
